parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall or accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or fires.
symptoms: The fuel pump continues to run after the engine is shut off
the vehicle stalls or accelerates unexpectedly
the fuel pump makes a humming or whining noise
the vehicle has difficulty starting or running
the fuel level in the tank is not high enough to properly cool the pump
which can cause overheating and potentially lead to a fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents or loss of control, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly
the vehicle jumps the curb or hits an obstacle
the vehicle's auto-braking system fails to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel system issues can cause the vehicle to stall or have difficulty starting, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The fuel pump makes a humming or whining noise
the vehicle has difficulty starting or running
the fuel level in the tank is not high enough to properly cool the pump
the vehicle stalls or has difficulty accelerating
the fuel system warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the RCD system can cause a lack of visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The RCD system displays an "unavailable" message
and the rear camera does not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unusual Loud Noise and Flashing Lights on Startup
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loud noise and flashing lights can startle the driver and potentially cause an accident.
symptoms: A loud
high-pitched sound is emitted when starting the vehicle
accompanied by flashing red and green lights next to the SOS button.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the climate control panel can cause a lack of defrosting and demisting capabilities, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The climate control panel does not function
resulting in no fan
heat
air conditioning
window defroster
mirror defroster
or seat heat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective sunroof can cause water to leak into the vehicle, leading to mold growth and potential electrical issues.
symptoms: The sunroof clogs
causing water to spill into the interior
and the driver-side sunroof tray drains become clogged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unreliable pre-collision warning system can cause the driver to rely on a faulty system, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The pre-collision warning system light turns on intermittently
indicating a faulty system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blind spot monitoring system can cause the driver to be unaware of vehicles in the blind spot, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The blind spot monitoring system on the passenger side does not function properly
failing to detect vehicles in the blind spot.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration can cause the vehicle to accelerate suddenly, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates and then accelerates spontaneously while driving in stop-and-go traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or jerking can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when accelerating from a stop or turning into traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting gears
especially at low speeds (less than 35 mph)
the transmission slips or feels like it's downshifting unexpectedly
the vehicle stalls or hesitates when accelerating from a stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission stalling can cause the vehicle to come to a sudden stop, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when accelerating from a stop or turning into traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when accelerating from a stop
especially at low speeds
the vehicle stalls when turning into traffic
the vehicle hesitates or jerks before shifting gears.
